  "text": "What about the physical examination syndrome? How does that relate to wanderers and to confederation in Orion contexts? The subconscious expectations of entities cause the nature and detail of thought, form, experience offered by confederation, thought, form, entities. Thus, if a wanderer expects a physical examination, it will per force be experienced with as little distortion towards alarm or a discomfort as is allowable by the nature of the expectations of the subconscious distortions of the wanderer.",
